  "title": "Industrial Engineer (Loyang/ 12 hours shift work)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Responsible to design, analyses and optimize complex systems to improve efficiency, productivity and quality.</li><li>Create and evaluate integrated systems that manage production processes, workflows and materials flow.</li><li>Identify bottlenecks, inefficiencies, and waste in existing processes and implement solutions, using lean principles and kaizens.</li><li>Use quantitative tools such as data analysis, statistics, and simulation modelling to guide decision making.</li><li>Develop and implement quality control processes to ensure products meet standards.</li><li>Considering human elements like ergonomics, safety and worker satisfaction when designing system.</li><li>Work with team members, supply chain and other departments to implement and monitor improvements.</li><li>Lead projects for process improvement, facility layout changes, system implementation, while managing timelines and budget.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Industrial/Manufacturing Engineering/Applied Science</li><li>Good communication, report writing and presentation skills</li><li>Good analytical skills with ability to work effectively</li><li>Independent, decisive and good in problem solving</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office</li><li>12 hours shift work</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Electronics Engineering</strong><br /><strong>Loyang Area</strong></p><p>Interested Applicants, kindly email your detailed resume to <a href=\"mailto:hr@tempserv.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>hr@tempserv.com.sg</strong></a></p><p><strong>Tempserv Pte Ltd</strong></p><p>License No: 06C3745</p><p><strong>Attention: Audris Teo / EA Personnel No: R1102063</strong></p>",
